  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2216600/extras/d95488994ee798af58019575ccb3fa26.poster.avif?t=1770264234\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2216600/extras/d95488994ee798af58019575ccb3fa26.webm?t=1770264234\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2216600/extras/d95488994ee798af58019575ccb3fa26.mp4?t=1770264234\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The Korea Dynasty</h2>The Joseon Dynasty ruled the Korean Peninsula from the 14th to the 20th century.<br><br>Korea was a centralized bureaucratic and Confucian state. And in terms of grographical location, it survived through diplomacy and war with great powers and successfully made outstanding cultures such as Hangeul as well as advanced science and technology.<br><br>On the other hand, there was inequality due to the strict status system, and there were so many people who starved even if they worked every day.<br><br>This game is an exploration and survival game composed of open world and contents by reconstructing the culture and geography of the Korea Dynasty.<br><br>You will begin as the slave of the Joseon Dynasty who learns survival skills, buys or steals identity to escape from a chased life.<br><br>Players can be a bandit, merchant, craftsman, bureaucrat or even explorer who search for historical sites in the whole world.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2216600/extras/0917af05ff61fd3f078a84cb45fc6f18.poster.avif?t=1770264234\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2216600/extras/0917af05ff61fd3f078a84cb45fc6f18.webm?t=1770264234\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2216600/extras/0917af05ff61fd3f078a84cb45fc6f18.mp4?t=1770264234\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>The lands of morning calm will be open! What would you choose?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Welcome to this game!</h2><br>This game is a survival/life game where you freely roam around a world recreated based on the culture of the Joseon Dynasty.<br><br>Here, you can draw a national map based on the actual topography of the Korean Peninsula, and travel anywhere on the Korean Peninsula.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2216600/extras/d97c5a083a0bdb214c9c33ae862a6fb6.poster.avif?t=1770264234\" width=600 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2216600/extras/d97c5a083a0bdb214c9c33ae862a6fb6.webm?t=1770264234\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2216600/extras/d97c5a083a0bdb214c9c33ae862a6fb6.mp4?t=1770264234\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>How will your future be written in a world where you have to do whatever you can, be it malicious, good, or intentional action in order to survive?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Features</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2216600/extras/d1a5402cfeeb63760211cba2591c4284.poster.avif?t=1770264234\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2216600/extras/d1a5402cfeeb63760211cba2591c4284.webm?t=1770264234\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2216600/extras/d1a5402cfeeb63760211cba2591c4284.mp4?t=1770264234\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>- 3000㎢ of open world, natural environment and islands</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2216600/extras/6aa8c73c706215bd04796c3ebc415860.poster.avif?t=1770264234\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2216600/extras/6aa8c73c706215bd04796c3ebc415860.webm?t=1770264234\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2216600/extras/6aa8c73c706215bd04796c3ebc415860.mp4?t=1770264234\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>- Various cities and castles</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2216600/extras/51e14b1f8bdd323b9f2c67df15039ce7.poster.avif?t=1770264234\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2216600/extras/51e14b1f8bdd323b9f2c67df15039ce7.webm?t=1770264234\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2216600/extras/51e14b1f8bdd323b9f2c67df15039ce7.mp4?t=1770264234\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>- More than 600 items and production methods from the Joseon Dynasty, including consumables, equipment, clothing, etc.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2216600/extras/0429363a7508017610a15abf9dc01fa5.poster.avif?t=1770264234\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2216600/extras/0429363a7508017610a15abf9dc01fa5.webm?t=1770264234\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2216600/extras/0429363a7508017610a15abf9dc01fa5.mp4?t=1770264234\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>- Joseon Dynasty style building system</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2216600/extras/453c203d5735206c993eab1f3c03dfcf.poster.avif?t=1770264234\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2216600/extras/453c203d5735206c993eab1f3c03dfcf.webm?t=1770264234\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2216600/extras/453c203d5735206c993eab1f3c03dfcf.mp4?t=1770264234\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>- More than a hundred relics of the Joseon Dynasty</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2216600/extras/60e454c6a55a36a17b8b9350bf717adc.poster.avif?t=1770264234\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2216600/extras/60e454c6a55a36a17b8b9350bf717adc.webm?t=1770264234\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2216600/extras/60e454c6a55a36a17b8b9350bf717adc.mp4?t=1770264234\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>- Quests, social influence with NPCs</strong><br><br><strong>- A trade system that allows you to make money using special products</strong><br><br><strong>- Co-op multiplayer</strong>",
